reviewText: My Mom has just about wore this DVD out!  I also love me some Lee Williams, and have this in my Amazon Music file.  Highly recommend for soul-stirring!
My grandmother can't stop playing it thanks..
I love the music from this group
You will definitely be having church with this cd/dvd set. I love their music. Definitely recommend it! It will draw you closer to the Lord!
I gave it as a gift and they really loved it
I ordered  the CD; you sent me the DVD the first time.  I returned it to you with a clear explanation.  You returned it to me a can in the form of a DVD.  I did not want a DVD, I wanted the CD.
